    <entry>
      <title>Add terms of use to redmine</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/24/Add-terms-of-use-to-redmine/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/24/Add-terms-of-use-to-redmine/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li>Install “Privacy &amp; Terms plugin for Redmine” <a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd $REDMINE_ROOT</span><br><span class="line">git clone git:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;alphanodes&#x2F;redmine_privacy_terms.git plugins&#x2F;redmine_privacy_terms</span><br><span class="line">git clone git:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;alphanodes&#x2F;additionals.git plugins&#x2F;additionals</span><br><span class="line">bundle install --without development test</span><br><span class="line">bundle exec rake redmine:plugins:migrate RAILS_ENV&#x3D;production</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>By above codes, you’ve also installed redmine plugin “additionals” which is also very useful.</li><li>Create a project to host wiki page of terms where everyone can access</li><li>Create wiki page of terms, optionally you can create a wiki page for users who reject the terms<br>“the two macros <code></code> and <code></code> must be implemented in it.”</li><li>Config <code>/settings/plugin/redmine_privacy_terms?tab=terms</code><br>URL of the wiki with the terms: <code>wiki/</code><br>URL of the wiki for users who reject the terms: external url or a wiki page (didnot work in my setting)<br>tick ‘Enable terms’</li><li>Check result in user profile page <code>/users/user-id</code>, and test accept/reject action.<ul><li>Terms of use<ul><li>Show</li><li>not acccepted yet</li></ul></li></ul></li><li>Optionally you can re-trigger request users to read and accept terms <code>/settings/plugin/redmine_privacy_terms?tab=tools</code><br>It’s done!</li></ol><p>Referenced from:</p><ol><li><a href="https://github.com/AlphaNodes/redmine_privacy_terms/blob/master/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/AlphaNodes/redmine_privacy_terms/blob/master/README.md</a></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
