    <entry>
      <title>Config redmine email smtp with outlook.com mail service</title>
      <link href="/2020/03/09/Config-redmine-email-smtp-with-outlook-com-mail-service/"/>
      <url>/2020/03/09/Config-redmine-email-smtp-with-outlook-com-mail-service/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li>edit redmine-root/config/configuration.yml<a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">production:</span><br><span class="line">  email_delivery:</span><br><span class="line">    delivery_method: :smtp</span><br><span class="line">    smtp_settings:</span><br><span class="line">      enable_starttls_auto: true</span><br><span class="line">      address: &quot;smtp.office365.com&quot;</span><br><span class="line">      port: 587</span><br><span class="line">      domain: &quot;outlook.com&quot;</span><br><span class="line">      authentication: :login</span><br><span class="line">      user_name: &quot;username@outlook.com&quot;</span><br><span class="line">      password: &quot;password&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>Restart your redmine daemon, options of “Administration : Email Notification” will be available.</li><li>Send a test email via redmine Administration : Email Notification tab<br>If you got error like “WASCL UserAction verdict is not None. Actual verdict is HipNotify, ShowTierUpgrade.”,<br>please check your outlook.com inbox and follow the guide to validate your Outlook.com account.<br>And try again.</li><li>Check your receiving email inbox or junk email, it’s done.</li></ol><p>Reference from:</p><blockquote><p>Here is an example for Office 365 users (Exchange online).</p><footer><strong>redmine, redmine.org</strong><cite><a href="https://www.redmine.org/projects/redmine/wiki/EmailConfiguration#Office-365-Exchange-Online" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Email Configuration</a></cite></footer></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
